Magazine Description

Everybody loves the glamour of entertainment: movies, music, TV shows, and the people who make them possible. From the red carpet to the movie screen, from stage to TV, eNews Magazine delivers hot content in digital entertainment every week, right to your fingertips. The main news is specially selected for those who enjoy and demand sophistication on a highly interactive level. With a tasteful vision, eNews Magazine will take the reader to a whole new sphere in the world of entertainment. Get your subscription now!
